diffrence betweeen error and exception?
Error :- it is like something that is caused due to some lack of resource. Ex - Stackoverflow
         Error basically non recoverable and program cannot handle it "we canot write code to handle it"
Exception :- it is something which handle the normal flow of program.
             something like: dividing something with zero(AirthmeticExceptoin,NullPointerException)
             you can recover this/check for these thing and program can handel it.

             flow char:-                        ____________>Exception ---> 1.checked(these are checked during the compile time/Exception during compile time it is a checked Exception)
                                                |                           2.Unchecked( when compiler will not able to detect that will only be detected while the program is running)
                                                |
                                                |
             object ---------> throwable -------
                                                |
                                                |
                                                |____________>Error


